cai ham fetch_url la
  given a url of text, returns the response body as text.
  can the url scheme is https.
  bao_dam the result is the response body without modification or yes-no failure.
  benefit cache_hit, fast_path.
  hazard timeout, dns_failure, tls_handshake_error.

cai ham search_web la
  given a query of text, returns a list of result links as text.
  can the query is non-empty.
  bao_dam the results are ordered by the underlying engine relevance.
  benefit index_hit.
  hazard rate_limited, upstream_error.
